        "content": "### Route by Event Kind\n\nRoutes each item to one of 3 lanes: job.start, job.done + fallback.\n\nPorts: ①→ Handle 'job.start' → Google Sheets · ②→ Handle 'job.done' → Forward API · ③→ Log Unrecognized Kind",
